Vendored diagram stencils
==========================

`stencils.json` in this directory contains shape geometry extracted from the
draw.io / diagrams.net stencil libraries (`stencils.min.js`).

  draw.io (diagrams.net) — https://github.com/jgraph/drawio
  Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.
  Copyright (c) JGraph Ltd.

The shapes are decoded from their base64/DEFLATE form and transcribed to SVG
path data + re-encoded `shape=stencil(...)` payloads by
`infra/tfs/scripts/extract_stencils.py`. The full provider palettes are vendored
(Google Cloud `gcp2`, AWS `aws4`, Azure `mscae`/`azure`, Kubernetes) so the
registry can map to any shape without re-running against the draw.io source;
adjust `SELECT_LIBS_*` in that script to add/trim libraries.

The icons depict third-party cloud-provider products and incorporate those
providers' trademarks (e.g. Google Cloud product icons). They are reproduced
solely to label the corresponding resources in architecture diagrams; all
trademarks remain the property of their respective owners.
